{"an6.23:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 6.23 ","an6.23:0.2":"3. Anuttariyavagga ","an6.23:0.3":"Bhayasutta ","an6.23:1.1":"“‘Bhayan’ti, bhikkhave, kamanametam adhivacanam; ","an6.23:1.2":"‘dukkhan’ti, bhikkhave, kamanametam adhivacanam; ","an6.23:1.3":"‘rogo’ti, bhikkhave, kamanametam adhivacanam; ","an6.23:1.4":"‘gando’ti, bhikkhave, kamanametam adhivacanam; ","an6.23:1.5":"‘sango’ti, bhikkhave, kamanametam adhivacanam; ","an6.23:1.6":"‘panko’ti, bhikkhave, kamanametam adhivacanam. ","an6.23:2.1":"Kasma ca, bhikkhave, ‘bhayan’ti kamanametam adhivacanam? ","an6.23:2.2":"Kamaragarattayam, bhikkhave, chandaragavinibaddho ditthadhammikapi bhaya na parimuccati, samparayikapi bhaya na parimuccati, tasma ‘bhayan’ti kamanametam adhivacanam. ","an6.23:2.3":"Kasma ca, bhikkhave, dukkhanti …pe… ","an6.23:2.4":"rogoti … ","an6.23:2.5":"gandoti … ","an6.23:2.6":"sangoti … ","an6.23:2.7":"pankoti kamanametam adhivacanam? ","an6.23:2.8":"Kamaragarattayam, bhikkhave, chandaragavinibaddho ditthadhammikapi panka na parimuccati, samparayikapi panka na parimuccati, tasma ‘panko’ti kamanametam adhivacananti. ","an6.23:3.1":"Bhayam dukkham rogo gando, ","an6.23:3.2":"sango panko ca ubhayam; ","an6.23:3.3":"Ete kama pavuccanti, ","an6.23:3.4":"yattha satto puthujjano. ","an6.23:4.1":"Upadane bhayam disva, ","an6.23:4.2":"jatimaranasambhave; ","an6.23:4.3":"Anupada vimuccanti, ","an6.23:4.4":"jatimaranasankhaye. ","an6.23:5.1":"Te khemappatta sukhino, ","an6.23:5.2":"ditthadhammabhinibbuta; ","an6.23:5.3":"Sabbaverabhayatita, ","an6.23:5.4":"sabbadukkham upaccagun”ti. ","an6.23:5.5":"Tatiyam. "}